Large-Scale Gains: For n>1e6. Pros: VRAM scales; Cons: Batch if overflow. Instr: Chunk: for i in range(batches): sim_chunk(). Snippet: chunk_size = 1e6; results = cp.concatenate([sim(i) for i in range(n//chunk_size)]).
